AFAnalysisTemplate.Name: Random Data
AFAnalysisTemplate.Description: Random Data Generation for State, Gas Flow and Fault Code

AFAnalysisRule.ConfigString: State := If Minute('*') >= 13 and Minute('*') <= 19 or Minute('*') >= 33 and Minute('*') <= 39 or Minute('*') >= 52 and Minute('*') <= 56 then "No Gas Flow" else "Gas Flow"; GasFlow := If '{b5ec31b1-b40b-4926-ba6d-4359b3312861};State' = "Gas Flow" then Abs(Rand(.015,.017)) else 0; FaultCode := If Minute('*') >= 23 and Minute('*') <= 29 then "Communication Failure" Else If Minute('*') >= 33 and Minute('*') <= 39 then "Valve Failure" Else If Minute('*') >= 42 and Minute('*') <= 46 then "Equipment Failure" else PrevVal('{b3c27209-a8ae-4af0-ab85-9a7c4b7eb9cd};Fault Code', '*'); GasFlowUnit := Convert(GasFlow, "ft3/s");
